dark ascension is an upcoming action/fantasy film directed by gene fallaize , executive produced by scott spiegel , and starring tara reid , brian blessed , paul blackthorne , and jillian murray , along with sean young , mackenzie crook , tony cook and serena lorien .   it follows the story of a group of recently deceased who arrive in the afterlife amidst a great war between heaven and hell .   it is the first part of a trilogy of films , with the first set to release in december 2017 .